        <abstract>
            <p>Representative species may complicate tabulation of varieties.</p>
            <p>Questions for Mr Anderson about horse colouring in Norway.</p>
            <p>Has been writing an "audacious little discussion" to show that "organic beings are not perfect, only perfect enough to struggle with their competitors".</p>
